00:00:39.070 --> 00:00:43.239
There are four main racial groups in TES series.

00:00:43.239 --> 00:00:46.710
Mer, Human, Akaviri and Beast races.

00:00:46.710 --> 00:00:50.540
Mer is a group of races, which can also be
called elves.

00:00:50.540 --> 00:00:57.030
The word "Mer" comes from the ancient Aldmeri
language and means "person" or "us."

00:00:57.030 --> 00:01:06.180
Its use by the elves is similar to our use
of the word "man", by which we describe any

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:09.990
human of any gender or skin color.

00:01:09.990 --> 00:01:14.380
Various elvish races have different opinions
on how they were created, but none of them

00:01:14.380 --> 00:01:19.660
consider the mortal life as a gift and many
of them actually think, that they are descendants

00:01:19.660 --> 00:01:25.720
of Aedra who lost their immortality during
the creation of the planet Nirn.

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:31.399
The elvish races usually live longer than
other races and are better attuned to the

00:01:31.399 --> 00:01:33.440
use of magic.

00:01:33.440 --> 00:01:38.940
The races in this group are:
Aldmer, Altmer, Ayleid, Bosmer, Chimer, Dunmer,

00:01:38.940 --> 00:01:42.850
Dwemer, Falmer, Maormer and Orsimer.

