00:01:59.030 --> 00:02:05.849
Anyway, Bretons could also be considered to
be elves, because they are a mixture of elves

00:02:05.849 --> 00:02:09.920
and men, but they are usually categorized
as men.

00:02:09.920 --> 00:02:14.900
Speaking of men, the group of races called
man or human, has no written account of their

00:02:14.900 --> 00:02:16.310
origin.

00:02:16.310 --> 00:02:21.640
They have evolved after the elvish races have,
but no one knows exactly how they came to

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:26.610
be, because the human races invented writing
much later.

00:02:26.610 --> 00:02:35.690
The human races are: Breton, Imperial, Nede,
Nord, Redguard, Orma and Kothringi.

00:02:35.690 --> 00:02:40.560
The third group of races are bestial races.

00:02:40.560 --> 00:02:46.530
These differ from the elven and human races
by the structure of their body and their metabolism.

00:02:46.530 --> 00:02:54.320
