00:03:17.730 --> 00:03:20.880
The last racial group is called Akaviri.

00:03:20.880 --> 00:03:26.350
Akaviri or Akavir, who knows whats the proper
form of the word, are a group of races living

00:03:26.350 --> 00:03:28.460
on the continent of Akavir.

00:03:28.460 --> 00:03:33.490
Not much is known about them, because people
of Tamriel dont visit the other continent

00:03:33.490 --> 00:03:35.100
too often.

00:03:35.100 --> 00:03:38.150
However, we know that they speak Akaviri.

00:03:38.150 --> 00:03:44.930
They consist of various types of races, both
man and beast, but some sources indicate,

00:03:44.930 --> 00:03:48.730
that the beast races have already taken care
of the human ones.

00:03:48.730 --> 00:03:52.630
Once again, no one knows for sure.

00:03:52.630 --> 00:03:59.520
Races in this group are: Kamal, Tsaesci, Ka
Po' Tun, Tang Mo and Dragons.

00:03:59.520 --> 00:04:05.240
